20
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:08,470
Xunrui,

21
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:11,190
are you looking for the Duan family vault?

22
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:13,590
What are you talking about?

23
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,800
I'm investigating something.

24
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,870
Stop lying.

25
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:18,430
We know everything.

26
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:19,560
We found the truth

27
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,800
behind the Duan family's murder.

28
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,680
This was all Song Zhenyuan's plan.

29
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:23,870
Huaining,

30
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,400
