31
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,190
So, you've been setting me up all along

32
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,190
to fall for this trap.

33
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,470
I've moved

34
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,910
everything in the vault away.

35
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:35,280
I don't know

36
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,240
what Song Zhenyuan told you
to make you trust him this much.

37
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,000
Xunrui,

38
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,280
we are real brothers.

39
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,400
He lied to you.

40
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,360
What proof do you have

41
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,560
that my godfather is using me?

42
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:43,840
Tell me.

43
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:45,680
Xunrui, calm down.

44
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:48,000
I'll explain everything to you.

45
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:51,280
Fine.

46
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:52,960
Fine.

47
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:01,520
Huaining.

48
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,080
Huaining, what's wrong?

49
00:03:03,190 --> 00:03:03,870
Are you alright?

50
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:05,910
Let her go.

51
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:07,750
If you don't want her dead,

52
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,560
put down your gun.

53
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,080
Put it down.

54
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,400
All of you, put your guns down.

55
00:03:35,310 --> 00:03:37,150
All of you, get out.

56
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:40,560
Out.

57
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,030
Huaining,

58
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,310
don't listen to Song Zhenyuan.

59
00:03:48,310 --> 00:03:49,800
He is your enemy.

60
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,590
Shut up.

61
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:55,960
Huaining,

62
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,150
are your headaches recurring?

63
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,280
Xunrui,

64
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,120
you won't hurt Wenyu.

65
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:10,120
Do you know?

66
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,750
The Duan family

67
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:14,750
is my real enemy.

68
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:18,000
I was never Duan Xunrui.

69
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:21,830
Song Zhenyuan planned everything all along

70
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,190
so I can get close to you.

71
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:25,680
During these years,

72
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,630
I had countless chance to kill you.

73
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:30,240
If he didn't want me to find the vault,

74
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,560
I would've already killed you.

75
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,830
Xunrui, he lied to you.

76
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:35,000
I have proof.

77
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:36,720
I have proof.

78
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,000
What proof do you have?

79
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:38,830
Adjutant Sun.

80
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:48,160
Director Wang?

81
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,600
It's true, Young Master.

82
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,920
They were telling the truth.

83
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:55,390
You really are Duan Xunrui.

84
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:58,360
After the explosion at the Duan mansion,

85
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,480
you lost your memories.

86
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:03,190
Song Zhenyuan thought you
know secrets about the vault,

87
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,430
so he adopted you.

88
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,920
When you kept investigating it,

89
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,160
you came up with nothing.

90
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:11,160
So, he had to make you
get close to Duan Xunchu.

91
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:13,190
In order to make you do it willingly,

92
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:14,750
he made up a story

93
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,160
to make you believe

94
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,680
that your parents were killed
by the Duan family.

95
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,000
Impossible.

96
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,800
Impossible.

97
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,120
You're lying.

98
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:33,630
He's lying, right?

99
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,190
No.

100
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,390
Impossible.

101
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,270
Impossible.

102
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:47,190
Impossible.

103
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,510
Impossible.

104
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,360
Thank you, Mother.

