00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:23,950
Huaining.

114
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,070
Xunrui.

115
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:31,430
Xunrui.

116
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:35,120
Huaining.

117
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,160
Huaining?

118
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,830
Xunrui.

119
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,720
Xunrui?

120
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,360
Xunrui.

121
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,630
Xunrui?

122
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:44,560
Xunrui.

123
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:54,680
Xunrui,

124
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,750
how do you feel?

125
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,630
Xunrui?

126
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,430
Duan Xunchu,

127
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,240
