128
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:05,600
You are my brother, Xunrui.

129
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:07,510
Director Wang's words,

130
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,120
the jade pendant,

131
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,800
and the birthmark on your back,

132
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,310
