133
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:14,830
Why wouldn't you admit it?

134
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,830
Huaining.

135
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,360
My father is Song Zhenyuan.

136
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,240
