145
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,920
There was also a rumor

146
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,830
that you are...

147
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,160
To trick me,

148
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,720
Duan Xunchu said I really am
his long-lost brother

149
